Examples: - "ðŸ¤– Auto-fix: fm-digitalguru-api-update-dlq-prod - Timeout in API calls" - "ðŸ¤– Auto-fix: fm-transaction-processor-dlq-prd - Database connection pool exhausted"
2. PR DESCRIPTION TEMPLATE: ```markdown ## ðŸš¨ Automated DLQ Investigation & Fix
**DLQ:** `{queue_name}` **Message Count:** {message_count} **Investigation Time:** {timestamp}
## ðŸ” Root Cause Analysis
**Issue Type:** {error_type} **Affected Component:** {component} **Frequency:** {error_frequency}
### Evidence - Error Pattern: {error_pattern} - CloudWatch Logs: {log_evidence} - Stack Trace: {stack_trace_summary}
## ðŸ› ï¸ Changes Made
### Files Modified - `path/to/file1.py` - {change_description} - `path/to/file2.py` - {change_description}
### Fix Details {detailed_fix_description}
## âœ… Testing
- [ ] Unit tests updated - [ ] Integration tests pass - [ ] Local testing completed - [ ] No breaking changes
## ðŸ“Š Impact
- **Before:** {problem_description} - **After:** {solution_description} - **Prevention:** {prevention_measures}
